What specific data are we collecting? How does it help predict player performance?
All of this is reference per game basis

Basketball
- PPG (Points per game)
- MPG (Minutes per game)
- Assists
- Blocks
- Steals
- 3-point %
- free throw %
- teams
-- average team offensive/defensive rating
-- team statistical percentages

Football (Soccer)
- Touches
- Shot attempts
- Free kicks allowed/attempted
- Passes
- Goals
- teams
-- average team offensive/defensive rating
-- team statistical percentages

Baseball
- Non-Pitcher
-- Hits
-- RBI
-- Stolen Bases
- Pitcher
-- Strikeouts
-- Batters Walked
-- Hits Allowed
- teams
-- average team offensive/defensive rating
-- team statistical percentages

American Football
- Quarterback
-- YPG (Yards per game) (both throwing and rushing)
- Running Back
-- YPG (Rushing, Receiving)
- Wide Receiver
-- YPG (Receiving)
- teams
-- average team offensive/defensive rating
-- team statistical percentages

APIs used:
https://api-sports.io/


Historical cap is last two seasons.
